WEBVTT

00:01.141 --> 00:03.041
- Punch Porsche red!
- Ow!

00:03.143 --> 00:04.859
Punch Porsche gray!

00:04.945 --> 00:06.745
What are you two lunatics doing?

00:06.846 --> 00:08.113
Playing Punch Buggy.

00:08.215 --> 00:10.649
Every time you see a Volkswagen Beetle,

00:10.751 --> 00:12.717
you yell out the color
and punch someone.

00:12.818 --> 00:14.152
But we made it Punch Porsche

00:14.254 --> 00:16.154
because in Westport,
there's more of those.

00:16.256 --> 00:17.522
Punch Porsche red!

00:17.624 --> 00:19.758
Ow! Punch Porsche gray!

00:19.860 --> 00:20.959
Your turn, Mrs. Otto!

00:21.061 --> 00:22.193
Ow!

00:22.296 --> 00:23.695
Franklin, new rule.

00:23.764 --> 00:25.730
Don't punch me
or anybody I'm related to.

00:25.832 --> 00:26.831
Unless it's Oliver

00:26.900 --> 00:28.566
and he's talking about French cuffs.

00:28.669 --> 00:30.302
Then go for it.

00:30.404 --> 00:32.671
Wait, that Porsche isn't even gray.

00:32.773 --> 00:33.905
Franklin, it's blue.

00:34.007 --> 00:37.676
I'm colorblind,
so everything looks gray to me.

00:37.778 --> 00:39.311
Punch Porsche gray!

00:39.413 --> 00:40.945
<i>Anna-Kat needs some new friends.</i>

00:41.048 --> 00:42.981
<i>Franklin talks weird, he dresses weird,</i>

00:43.083 --> 00:44.716
<i>he even sees color weird.</i>

00:44.818 --> 00:46.551
<i>He's like the Michael Jordan
of not fitting in.</i>

00:46.620 --> 00:50.722
How about at lunch today,
you don't sit by yourselves?

00:50.824 --> 00:52.424
Invite some new people to join you.

00:52.526 --> 00:54.192
Nah. I won't go into detail,

00:54.294 --> 00:55.955
but kids don't like
to watch Franklin eat.

00:57.130 --> 00:58.863
Ugh. Damn it!

00:58.932 --> 00:59.979
We're out of gas.

01:00.049 --> 01:02.100
Taylor took the car out again
without filling it up.

01:05.105 --> 01:06.705
- Punch Porsche gray!
- If you do it,

01:06.773 --> 01:08.640
you better knock me out,
'cause I'm gonna punch back.

